## How to Run
To predict on new images:
```bash
python3 inference.py /path/to/your/image.jpg
```

## Accuracy by Class
Evaluated on 1,986 test images:

| CLASS | ACCURACY |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Clothes** | **99.06%** |
| Shoes | 96.98% |
| Biological (Food) | 96.04% |
| Paper | 95.83% |
| Battery | 94.79% |
| Glass | 94.46% |
| Cardboard | 93.44% |
| Plastic | 91.50% |
| Trash | 90.62% |
| Metal | 90.20% |
| **OVERALL** | **95.37%** |

